SEASONALITY 

In &#160;

general, &#160;

demand &#160;

for &#160;

our &#160;

products &#160;

is &#160;

evenly &#160;

balanced &#160;

throughout &#160;

the &#160;

year. &#160;

However, &#160;

within &#160;

our &#160;

North &#160;

America &#160;

Retail &#160;

segment 

demand &#160;

for &#160;

refrigerated &#160;

dough, &#160;

frozen &#160;

baked &#160;

goods, &#160;

and &#160;

baking &#160;

products &#160;

is &#160;

stronger &#160;

in &#160;

the &#160;

fourth &#160;

calendar &#160;

quarter. &#160;

Demand &#160;

for 

Progresso 

soup is higher &#160;

during the &#160;

fall and winter &#160;

months. Within &#160;

